  "message": "test(ufunc): extend neg/abs/max metamorphic relations with edge cases\n\nAdded 9 fixtures broadening the three thin ufunc metamorphic\nrelations (each previously had 2 cases):\n\n- neg_involution (3 new): 1-D with \u00b10 and \u00b1denormals (5e-324),\n  large magnitudes \u00b11e300/\u00b11e-300, empty 1-D (shape=[0])\n- abs_idempotent (3 new): all-negative 3-D (2x2x2), -0.0-preserves\n  against +0.0 and small magnitudes, empty 2-D (shape=[0,3])\n- max_commutative (3 new): equal-values everywhere (tie path),\n  all-negative inputs, scalar broadcast (rhs shape=[])\n\n48 ufunc_metamorphic cases total (from 39).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
